                    </div>
                    <p>Electric field is vector quantity hence it's added by superposition principle. The superposition principle says that if multiple vectors act on a point, the overall effect is the vector sum of all of them.</p>
                    <div class="math-block">
                        \\[\\mathbf{E}_{\\mathrm{p}} = \\mathbf{E}_{\\mathrm{p1}} + \\mathbf{E}_{\\mathrm{p2}} + \\mathbf{E}_{\\mathrm{p3}} + \\mathbf{E}_{\\mathrm{p4}}\\]
