                    <div class="math-block">
                        \\[\\mathbf{E}_{\\mathrm{p}} = k\\sum_{i = 1}^{n}\\frac{q_{i}}{(r_{pi})^{2}}\\hat{\\mathbf{r}}_{pi}\\]
