                        \\[E = \\frac{kq}{(r + a)^2} (-\\hat{x}) + \\frac{kq}{(r - a)^2}\\hat{x}\\]
                        \\[E = kq\\left(\\frac{1}{(r - a)^2} - \\frac{1}{(r + a)^2}\\right)\\hat{x}\\]
