                        \\[E_{-q} = \\frac{kq}{(\\sqrt{r^2 + a^2})^2} = \\frac{kq}{r^2 + a^2} = E\\]
                        \\[\\cos \\theta = \\frac{a}{\\sqrt{r^2 + a^2}}\\]
                    </div>
                    <div class="math-block">
                        \\[E_p = E\\cos \\theta \\hat{x} + E\\cos \\theta \\hat{x}\\]
                        \\[E_p = 2E\\cos \\theta \\hat{x}\\]
                        \\[E_p = 2\\frac{kq}{r^{2} + a^{2}}\\cos \\theta \\hat{x}\\]
                        \\[E_p = 2\\frac{kq}{r^{2} + a^{2}}\\frac{a}{\\sqrt{r^{2} + a^{2}}}\\hat{x}\\]
                        \\[E_p = \\frac{2kqa}{(r^{2} + a^{2})^{3/2}}\\hat{x}\\]
                    </div>
                    <p>For \\(r \\gg a\\) (far away point):</p>
                    <div class="math-block">
                        \\[E_p = \\frac{2kqa}{r^3}\\hat{x}\\]
                        \\[E_p = \\frac{k(2qa)}{r^3}\\hat{x}\\]
